  "texts": [
    "Finally, the study involved students from the same university with similar backgrounds, so including a more diverse group of participants could improve the generalizability of the findings.",
    "Future research should explore the long-term impacts of AI integration in education, examining how different types of AI tools can be tailored to support diverse learner profiles effectively.",
    "Additionally, investigating the factors that influence the plateau in performance gains, the role of task complexity, and potential challenges of AI tool nature in shaping learning outcomes can provide deeper insights into optimizing AI-enhanced learning environments.",
    "Studies could also examine how regional disparities in AI access and digital literacy impact programming education outcomes, contributing to more equitable integration strategies across diverse educational settings.",
    "Addressing these gaps may require tailored support to ensure students worldwide benefit equitably from advancements in AI-driven programming education."
